# 📝 Task 04 - To-Do Web App

This is a basic **To-Do List Web Application** developed as part of **Task 4** for the Web Development Internship at **Skillcraft**.

The app allows users to:
- Add and organize tasks
- Set date and time for each task
- Mark tasks as completed
- Edit or delete tasks
- Maintain an interactive and responsive task list

---

## 🔧 Technologies Used

- **HTML5**
- **CSS3**
- **Vanilla JavaScript**

---

## ✨ Features

- 📌 **Add Tasks** — Easily create new tasks with a title, description, date, and time  
- ✅ **Mark as Completed** — Toggle tasks between completed and pending  
- ✏️ **Edit Tasks** — Modify task details any time  
- ❌ **Delete Tasks** — Remove tasks from the list  
- 🕒 **Set Deadline** — Attach date & time to each task for reminders  
- 📱 **Responsive Design** — Works on both desktop and mobile screens  

